1
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,920
This is the fine spot Master Ai picked for you

2
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,560
Looks ordinary to me

3
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,040
This Master Ai isn't some swindler, is he?

4
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,280
No

5
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:11,440
Master Ai is very effective

6
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:14,440
Ever since Meigu suddenly left a year ago

7
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:17,200
her apprentice has run the Feng Shui Hall

8
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,200
The Wan family that runs the pawnshop

9
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,200
the Li family at the bank

10
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,320
the Wang family at the pharmacy

11
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,400
she found auspicious sites for them all

12
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,680
Their businesses keep getting better

13
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,240
She's even more capable than Meigu

14
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:30,000
Our Lü family also went through a lot

15
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,880
before we got Master Ai to come out

16
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,120
Master Ai has arrived

17
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,160
Let me introduce him

18
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:57,080
This is Mr. Zheng, here for the Bone-collecting ritual

19
00:01:57,760 --> 00:02:00,480
Mr. Zheng, do you think I, Ai, am a fraud?

20
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,800
This place seems terribly inauspicious

21
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,640
but its position is most unusual

22
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,440
So long as the rite is done

23
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,160
it becomes a rare auspicious site

24
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:12,720
Only then can the Fox Spirit's resentment be quelled

25
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,720
So that's how it is

26
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,640
Master Ai, what insight

27
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,080
I am impressed

28
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:21,440
Master Ai, look

29
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:24,000
We've done everything as you said

30
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,600
As for our Lü family being cursed by the Fox Spirit

31
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,640
that can finally be put to rest now, yes?

32
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,360
The remains can be moved

33
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,080
The curse can also be removed

34
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:47,640
But so long as vicious hearts remain

35
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,840
the Lü family will know no peace

36
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,120
At this hour of the night

37
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,920
where are we going dressed like this?

38
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,640
During yesterday's Bone-collecting ritual

39
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,760
I heard the Lü servants say

40
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,600
that Lü Quan offended the Fox Spirit

41
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:09,960
I also heard Lü Quan has strange tastes

42
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,480
After he gets drunk

43
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,000
he likes to take girls from the dance hall

44
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,000
to do that sort of thing near the Fox Spirit's grave

45
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,840
and even curse at the tombstone

46
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,560
and piss on it

47
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:20,040
That's what enraged the Fox Spirit

48
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,480
So then

49
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,920
Lü Quan should have been the Fox Spirit's first target

50
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:25,920
Exactly

51
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,800
You mean

52
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,720
there's more about Lü Quan we don't know?

53
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,760
We're almost at the Paramount Ballroom

54
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,000
Whether he has secrets

55
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,480
we'll know once we go meet him

56
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,280
Come on

57
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,320
Let's find a place to sit first

58
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,920
Lü Quan

59
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,000
Get out of my way

60
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,560
You really are beyond saving

61
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:31,000
You did not even return for the Matriarch's funeral

62
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,280
and came here to fool around again

63
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,720
She was arrogant and overbearing

64
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:37,000
and even indirectly caused Fourth Madam Wang's death

65
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:40,320
Now the Fox Spirit has come to claim her life

66
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,920
She had it coming

67
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,960
You jerk

68
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:49,560
Do you even still see me as your uncle?

69
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,480
Before your mother died of illness, she urged me again and again

70
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,200
to take good care of you

71
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,000
Come with me

72
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,960
Are you addicted to putting on this act?

73
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,920
Don't think I don't know

74
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:07,440
what your real purpose is in staying with our Lü family

75
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,280
You

76
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,000
Men

77
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,520
Throw him out

78
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,600
You... Lü Quan

79
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,600
You... Lü Quan

80
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,520
Stop staring

81
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:18,920
Keep dancing

82
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,280
Do not be angry, Young Master Lü

83
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,400
This Lü Quan is truly no good

84
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,840
Sir, your drink. Thank you

85
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,160
Thank you

86
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,440
But the girls at the Paramount Ballroom are truly fine

87
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:34,280
I brought you here to watch Lü Quan

88
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,240
not to ogle the girls beside you

89
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,080
I am watching, aren't I?

90
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,560
Sorry, sorry, Young Master Lü

91
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,640
Let me wipe it for you

92
00:05:57,920 --> 00:06:00,640
Drink the wine and I'll forgive you

93
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:00,880
I...

94
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,360
I cannot drink

95
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,760
Cannot drink?

96
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:08,200
Then I will feed it to you myself

97
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,720
Young Master, I truly cannot drink

98
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,920
Wait, please spare me

99
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,800
I will drink the girl's wine

100
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,440
Why has she come?

101
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:54,640
How could we let Young Master Lü be disappointed?

102
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:58,760
I'll sing a tune for Young Master Lü to liven things up

103
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,760
Young master

104
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,400
Who... who is that?

105
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:30,920
She's new here today

106
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,560
They said she was sent down from above

107
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,880
I couldn't pry further

108
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,120
Young master

109
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,520
Stop the crew-cut man and the fat one behind her

110
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,880
Only Young Master Lü may enter. Yes

111
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,720
Just to see Young Master Lü once

112
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,400
it really wasn't easy

113
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,600
Since I can get in

114
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,720
next time I'll buy you a drink

115
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,600
Make way, make way

116
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:41,600
Miss, you know me?

117
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,080
Of course

118
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:47,200
I just wonder if Young Master Lü remembers me

119
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,240
Then let me see

120
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:53,880
Which little beauty of mine are you?

121
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,040
You...

122
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,720
Aren't you...

123
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:06,520
No, that's not right

124
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,920
You're her twin sister

125
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,400
So Young Master Lü still remembers my sister

126
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,960
Now you're here drowning in pleasure

127
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:20,560
while my sister's lone soul cannot rest, Young Master Lü

128
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:24,400
Have you ever felt even a shred of guilt for her?

129
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,800
I...

130
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,920
I did wrong by her

131
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:31,680
But... but

132
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,560
But I did all I could

133
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,520
It was them

134
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,520
Ye-yes, they were the ones who harmed your sister

135
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,360
Young Master Lü

136
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,680
If you feel guilty toward my sister

137
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:45,120
then tell me what really happened

138
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:47,440
It was Wang Shengchang

139
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:52,320
Every three years, he carries out a Sacrifice

140
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,680
A sacrifice of what?

141
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,800
No, why is she allowed to go in?

142
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,120
Something's wrong

143
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:22,080
The Lü family's young master is possessed by the Fox Spirit
